'''Tu'ana''' was a city on [[Terephon]]. Tu'ana's official sent notice to [[Hapan Fleet Ops]] to inform [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Grand Master/Legends|Grand Master]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] that unregistered and unidentified [[Ship (Sith Meditation Sphere)|ship]] reported by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] was removed without city's authorization while in their jurisdiction.

